Help Type: topic
Topic: troubleshoot

Troubleshooting

No search results:
  Try fewer keywords, use a broader URI, or inspect chapter readiness and structure with:
    wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter
    wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter/tree

Missing generated objects:
  Queue the relevant generation task for the chapter:
    wikigraph wikg://local/job add --input <chapter-uri> --task reading-graph --accept-cost
    wikigraph wikg://local/job add --input <chapter-uri> --task reading-summary --accept-cost

Need machine-readable output:
  Use `--json` or `--jsonl` on object commands.
  Read `wikigraph help retrieval` for pagination and output format choices.

URI rejected:
  Do not pass a bare filesystem path to object commands. Convert it first:
    /Users/me/book.wikg -> wikg:///Users/me/book.wikg
  If you copied a short URI such as `wikg://entity/Q8018` from output, prepend the archive locator:
    wikg:///Users/me/book.wikg/entity/Q8018

Help did not appear:
  Append `--help` to the URI or command you are trying to inspect:
    wikigraph wikg://book.wikg/chapter --help
    wikigraph wikg://book.wikg/entity/Q8018 --help
